{"tid":1441049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［好爆但冇人理］「元首級淫媒」艾普斯坦　獄中自殺身亡","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:16:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd7a6ec68050ad2d28b73934abdf4d4f9da5524","tid":1441049,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzLQhoQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqzLQhoQ.jpg&h=f64afd75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/10/224241_54c60d4c2768274839888bd4e34fa321.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2F224241_54c60d4c2768274839888bd4e34fa321.jpeg&h=874e267c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/10/224242_ec78fb2fcf33ab447449ff8e25799f8a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2F224242_ec78fb2fcf33ab447449ff8e25799f8a.jpeg&h=26b99bda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/10/224244_1bc4d894dc8f342234cb6e434af91ee5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2F224244_1bc4d894dc8f342234cb6e434af91ee5.png&h=4257d2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟美國總統川普交好、有「元首級淫媒」之稱的美國富商艾普斯坦（ Jeffrey Epstein ），今（ 10 ）日被發現在獄中自殺身亡。艾普斯坦在上午 7 點半左右，被獄方人員發現上吊自殺。美國媒體報導稱，他在上個月 24 日也曾在獄中自殺未遂。<br />\n<br />\n66 歲的艾普斯坦是知名華爾街投資銀行家，在 80 年代經濟蓬勃發展時，迅速累積財富，財富橫跨各國，與眾多政商名流交好。外界盛傳，他用約 1000 美元（約新台幣 30000 元）的價碼，誘騙未成年少女到他家發生性關係，並且仲介未成年女子給他的政商名流好友們。艾普斯坦曾在 2005 年遭到逮捕，被查出有 40 多名女子淪為他的性奴，當時他選擇認罪協商，入獄服刑 13 個月。<br />\n<br />\n這次他再度被捕，隨著爆料者越來越多，艾普斯坦的性醜聞牽涉之廣，已到元首等級，包括美國現任總統川普、前總統柯林頓、英國安德魯王子等名人都是。其中有兩名受害人表示，曾被艾普斯坦強迫做性奴，「服務對象」則是英國安德魯王子。一名叫羅伯茨（ Virginia Roberts Giuffre ）詳細描述了被艾普斯坦和英國名媛麥克斯韋爾（ Ghislaine Maxwell ）強迫當「性奴」的 3 年痛苦經歷。她與安德魯王子的合照也跟著曝光，當時她年僅 17 歲。<br />\n<br />\n白金漢宮對此事強烈否認。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20190810/3558484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20190810%2F3558484%2F&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMnza4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=23453f72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20190810/3558484/</a><br />\n<br />\nJeffrey Epstein Commits Suicide at Manhattan Jail, Officials Say<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/10/nyregion/jeffrey-epstein-suicide.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2Fnyregion%2Fjeffrey-epstein-suicide.html&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMnza4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=8dc8003c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/10/nyregion/jeffrey-epstein-suicide.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b247e8e3aa0f90d01b565814940caea37acd52a","tid":1441049,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"個關係網好撚多猶太人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaa373301a56b7087cf27974bcf47860acb4c91","tid":1441049,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"唔信係自殺"},{"pid":"b72b382886ee704e64da41683cdf47382270d197","tid":1441049,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcaa373301a56b7087cf27974bcf47860acb4c91","tid":1441049,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"唔信係自殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"知得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2811f4abac333c23983463886efabb7fa85ff92d","tid":1441049,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b72b382886ee704e64da41683cdf47382270d197","tid":1441049,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcaa373301a56